snippet.title: Strange Horticulture - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Become aquainted with Strange Horticulture's dark mysteries through the story trailer! Strange Horticulture is an occult puzzle game in which you play as the proprietor of a local plant store. Find and identify new plants, pet your cat, speak to a coven, or join a cult. Use your collection of powerful plants to influence the story and unravel Undermere’s dark mysteries.

WISHLIST on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1574580/Strange_Horticulture/
